            bindings = <
        &kp EXCL  &kp AT  &kp HASH  &kp DLLR      &kp PRCNT            &kp CARET         &kp AMPS      &kp ASTERISK  &Autopair_Paren  &kp EQUAL
        &trans    &trans  &trans    &line_select  &selection_search    &kp C_PLAY_PAUSE  &kp C_PREV    &kp C_NEXT    &kp MINUS        &kp SEMICOLON
&trans  &trans    &trans  &trans    &trans        &trans               &kp C_MUTE        &kp QUESTION  &kp SLASH     &trans           &trans         &Autopair_Quotes
                          &trans    &trans        &trans               &trans            &trans        &trans
